本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:方立維研究生(外文):Fang Li-Wei論文名稱:中國大陸公司治理與內部控制制度問題之研究論文名稱(外文):A Study on Corporate Governance and Internal Control in China指導教授:何曜琛指導教授(外文):J.D. Spenser Y. Hor學位類別:碩士校院名稱:中國文化大學系所名稱:法律學研究所學門:法律學門學類:一般法律學類論文出版年:2005畢業學年度:94語文別:中文論文頁數:347中文關鍵詞:公司治理、內部控制、獨立董事、股東權益外文關鍵詞:corporate governance、internal control、independent directors、shareholder’s rights and business information disclosure相關次數:

被引用:6點閱:367評分:下載:0書目收藏:4



大陸基於社會主義制度下之歷史因素，多數企業皆由國營企業而來，國企改革向來為其濫觴。自2000年開始，大陸在公司治理方面進行了一系列的改革，在國際資金投資越趨密切下，受到自由市場經濟制度催化，大陸國務院已將促進股市發展及強化公司治理列為重點工作，觀乎2005年10月修正之公司法及證券法便以此為修法原則。大陸公司治理發展基於分權制衡概念，較先進國家多屬公司治理結構的層面，較註重於公司股東大會、董事會、監事會和高層經營者之間的制衡關係，缺乏側重於公司內部治理結構方面。治理結構雖無法全然解決公司治理所有問題，但目前大陸亟需建立具法制性及有效性之公司治理結構的環境下，相關主管機關更需有制訂超越現行結構的配套政策。本文就大陸上市公司治理之部分關係以內部控制制度為出發點解析，包含（1）股東與股東大會：含括股東權利保護與股東大會規範二部分；（2）董事和董事會：含括董事義務、獨立董事、董事會規範三部分；（3）資訊公開；（4）監事與監事會含括監事會的組成及職權、監事會議事規則；（4）上市公司績效評價與激勵約束機制；（5）新修正公司法與證券法概述等部分加以解析，以為論述大陸公司治理相關法規現況。自博達案後，我國金管會開始正視公司治理及強化內部控制的議題，鼓勵自願設置的方式來取代證券交易法的強制要求，要求所有上市（櫃）公司設立獨立董監之最低標準。觀諸大陸近年經濟與市場發展，資金之吐納與集中市場規模相悖甚遠。突顯大陸公司治理下所衍生的狀態，確有值得考慮的空間。以兩岸同文同種的性質，不論從公司治理所肩負的功能、強化內部控制制度卻屬必要。兩岸在可見未來，經貿關係勢必更為熱絡，他山之石，可以攻錯。

Due to the historical reason of socialism, many enterprises in China stemmed from the state-owned enterprises.  In 2000, China commenced a series of innovations for corporate governance.  In the circumstances of more international investments, as well as under the influence of an open-market economic system, the promotion of securities market and enhancement of corporate governance have been regarded as important issues by General Office of State Council.  The Company Law and Securities Law promulgated in October 2005 were amended according to the aforesaid rule.  In consideration of separation of powers, the development of corporate governance in China, compared to the one in developed countries, is more focused on the structure of corporate governance and the relationships among the shareholders, the board of directors, the supervisory committee and the high level officers.  The development of corporate governance in China lacks of the internal governance structure.  The governance structure may not resolve all questions relating to the corporate governance.  China, at present, urgently needs to establish an environment with legal and effective corporate governance structure, and the competent authorities will have to set up complete policies that surpass the current structure. This thesis mainly analyzed the internal control of corporate governance of the listed Chinese companies, in which includes (1) the part of shareholders and the shareholder meeting contains the protection for shareholder rights and the norm for the shareholder meeting; (2) the part of directors and director board meeting contains the directors’ obligation, the independent directors and the norm of the board of directors; (3) the business information disclosure; (4) the part of supervisors and supervisor meeting contains their composition, obligation and the rule for supervisor meeting; (5) the appraisal of the listed company performance and internal employee control; and (6) the structure of the amended Company Law and Securities Law.  The above sections analyze the current corporate governance in China.After Procomp Informatics Ltd. case, the Taiwan Financial Supervisory Commission commenced to pay attention to the issue of corporate governance and internal control and encouraged the principle of voluntary corporate governance rather than compulsory enforcement by the Securities and Exchange Law.  Noticing the recent economical and marketing development in China, the scale between capital and financial market is with discrepancy. This discrepancy leads us to reconsider the corporate governance problems in China.  As Taiwan and China stem from the same race and use the same language, the enhancement of corporate governance is necessary.  The commercial relations between Taiwan and China in the future will be tighter, and we shall observe the corporate governance development in China.

