118頁


口試委員
指導教授-陳淑惠
口試委員-鄭文英
口試委員-張淑昭



關鍵字(中)
在宅安養高齡者智慧生活


關鍵字(英)
The ElderlyAging-in-PlaceSmart Life


學科別分類



中文摘要
　　隨著經濟結構的變化、醫療技術的進步、教育程度的提高、家庭結構的改變、女性進入職場等社會現象的影響，越來越多的國家面臨了高齡少子化所帶來的種種衝擊，當然我國也不例外。人口老化帶來的最重要的社會問題，即是撫養比率增高、勞動市場的供給減少以及人口結構老化，而少子化的趨勢更讓這個問題雪上加霜。在現今社會中科技發展之快速，已經使得高齡者無法避免於日常生活中使用各種科技產品。因此如何以科技輔助高齡者也越來越受到重視。設計適合高齡者的科技產品與服務，改進其生活與工作環境及健康照護，使得高齡者能夠獨立、健康、快樂地享受生活。　　本研究期望藉由文獻探討，以瞭解高齡者「在宅安養」的需求，並從需求點導入智慧生活的應用，對高齡者與智慧生活領域之專家發放專家問捲，並以AHP層級分析法進行各層級的需求權重計算。透過所得之需求權重，分階段進行高齡者「在宅安養」之智慧生活導入，以減少科技對於高齡者「在宅安養」之衝擊，以提升高齡者對於智慧生活的接受度。以下三點為本研究之主要內容有：1.	智慧生活應用於高齡者「在宅安養」之趨勢發展架構2.	智慧生活應用於高齡者「在宅安養」之趨勢發展系統3.	智慧生活應用於高齡者「在宅安養」推展議題之探討　　透過各階層之需求權重可瞭解，對於高齡者「在宅安養」導入智慧生活，最重要的是能滿足高齡者移動安全的需求，其次依序為防災安全、身體健康照護與防犯安全、便利生活、健康舒適環境以及心理健康照護。由此可知「安全」乃是專家最重視的領域，特別是移動安全。因此對於智慧生活產業的推動者，初期應掌握智慧化的「移動安全」與智慧化的「防災安全」；後期將其他需求分階段或分客群進行智慧生活導入。


英文摘要
Owing to the present phenomena influence on the changing of economic structure, advancing in medical skill, improving on education, changing in family structure, and entering job market by female, more and more countries face the impact by aging society, including Taiwan. Aging society brings serious social problems in the world. On the conditions of lots of families raising more children, the diminishing of labor market and demographic structure aging still can not solve the problem of aging society. The trend of fewer children makes this issue worse. Technology has developed rapidly in recent society and it makes aging people hardly to avoid using high tech appliances in their daily life. Therefore how to use high tech appliance to help the Elderly becomes an important issue. Design high tech products and provide service for the Elderly not only improving their lives, working environment, healthy care but also making the Elderly feel more independent, healthier, and happier to enjoy their lives.  This research expects using literature review to understand “Aging-in-Place” need for the Elderly and introduce Smart Life from the demanding. Having interview with experts and scholars, who specialize in aging people and Smart Life field, send them questionnaires and using AHP methodology calculates the ratio later. According to the figure of ratio that I got from this study, introduce Smart Life into “Aging-in-Place” for the Elderly to reduce the impact on the Elderly homecare and increase acceptance of Smart Life to the Elderly. This study mainly focuses on three research purposes:  1.The trend of Smart Life’s developing framework applies to “Aging-in-Place” for the Elderly.  2.The trend of Smart Life’s developing system applies to “Aging-in-Place” for the Elderly.  3.The exploring issue of Smart Life applies to “Aging-in-Place” for the Elderly.  First, the most important issue is to satisfy moving safety for aging people by understanding the ratio from different layers and introduce “Aging-in-Place” to the Elderly. Second, it is anti-disaster safety, physical health care, anti-crime, convenient life, comfortable environment, and mental healthy care. So “Safety” is the only thing that experts care, especially moving safety. Therefore the people, who promote Smart Life business, should focus on moving safety and anti-disaster safety at beginning. Later the promoter shall separate the needs by different stages or customers to proceed and introduce Smart Life.


論文目次
